name: Sienna Miller
description:
We have a revelation about Sienna Miller.

You know, Sienna Miller, the rather gorgeous, rather thin, rather British actress, who can't seem to leave the pages of British tabloids.

She is American!

That's right, Miller was born in New York, but moved to London at a very young age.

What, did you think we were going to tell you that she is Jewish?

Don't believe the tabloids.
